						<div align=left id="content-works">
							<h2>Touch Hands: a table grace</h2>
							<b>Voicing:</b> round, partner song or double canon<br>
							<b>Text:</b> W.H.H. Murray<br>
							<b>Language:</b> English<br>
							<b>Duration:</b> varies<br>
							<b>Premiere:</b> The MPR Carolers, Minnesota Public Radio - Dec. 22, 2017<br>
							<b>Published by:</b> Abbie Betinis Music Co., AB-106-C17<br>
							<br>
							<b>Available in:</b> Print or Digital Edition (<a href="../order_form.html">order the score</a>)<br>
							<br>
							<br>
							<span class="works-headers">LISTEN</span>
							<div class="works-body">
							Performed by the MPR Carolers: <br>
							<span class="resume-small">Laura Betinis Healy (alto solo), Carrie Henneman Shaw, Nicholas Chalmers, Timothy C Takach</span><br>
							<br>
